# Black Flag Design Brand Guidelines

> **Playful. Confident. Clear.**

This document defines the visual identity system for Black Flag Design. All implementations MUST follow these specifications exactly.

---

## Brand Essence

### Tagline

**"Software so good you can't help but smile."**

This tagline embodies our mission — building software that delights through quality and craft. The smile is earned, not manufactured.

### Tone & Voice

| Attribute | Description |
|-----------|-------------|
| **Playful** | We take our work seriously, not ourselves |
| **Confident** | We know our craft and it shows in the details |
| **Clear** | We say what we mean without jargon |
| **Honest** | Direct, no-BS communication |
| **Warm** | Approachable, never intimidating |

### Design Philosophy

- **Monochromatic base with playful pops** — Clean black/white foundation, strategic color for delight
- **Generous white space** — Let content breathe, avoid density
- **Compact type scale** — Montserrat for clarity, JetBrains Mono for code
- **Subtle rounding** — 4px-12px radii for friendly but professional feel
- **Comic shadows for personality** — Hard offset shadows on sticky notes and playful elements

