## Subtle Rounding (NOT Sharp Corners)

Unlike HW's zero-radius policy, BFD uses **subtle rounding** for a friendly-but-professional feel:

| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| `radius-sm` | 4px | Small inputs, tags |
| `radius-md` | 8px | Cards, buttons |
| `radius-lg` | 12px | Modals, large containers |
| `radius-xl` | 16px | Hero cards, feature highlights |

Never use fully rounded (`rounded-full`) on containers. Reserve it for avatars and small badges only.

