### Comic Shadow Rules

- `shadow-comic` is the signature BFD personality element
- Use ONLY on sticky notes, playful callouts, and informal elements
- NEVER on primary UI chrome (nav, modals, form inputs)
- Always pair with a solid border (`border-3` or `border-4`) and slight rotation for hand-placed feel

