## Logo System

### The Mark

The Black Flag Design mark is 6 horizontal bars + a canton (solid rectangle, upper-right). Aspect ratio: **2:1** (280×140 viewBox).

| Variant | File | Usage |
|---------|------|-------|
| **Dark** | `public/logos/mark-dark.svg` | Light backgrounds (`#171717` fill) |
| **Light** | `public/logos/mark-light.svg` | Dark backgrounds (`#F2F2F2` fill) |

### Logo Rules

- Minimum size: **24×12 pixels** (preserve legibility of 6 bars)
- Clear space: At least 1x mark height on all sides
- Never stretch, rotate, or add effects (drop shadow, glow, etc.)
- The canton is always upper-right — never mirror the mark

