### Sticky Notes

The signature BFD playful element:
- Yellow/green/purple backgrounds from the Pop palette
- `border-3` solid border, `#171717`
- `shadow-comic` hard offset shadow
- Slight CSS rotation (±1-3deg) for hand-placed feel
- Never use on formal UI — only callouts, tips, and personality moments

### Cards

- `bg-bf-surface` or `bg-bf-bg`
- `rounded-xl` (12px)
- `shadow-card` → `shadow-card-hover` on hover
- `border border-bf-border` optional

