## Forbidden Patterns

### ❌ NEVER DO

**Color Prohibitions:**
- Use Pop colors (yellow, green, purple) as primary UI backgrounds
- Use `shadow-comic` on formal UI elements (buttons, nav, modals)
- Mix dark mode and light mode tokens in the same component without a toggle

**Typography Prohibitions:**
- Use fonts other than Montserrat and JetBrains Mono
- Use uppercase on anything except Captions
- Use weight 600 for primary text (reserved for strong emphasis only)

**Layout Prohibitions:**
- Use `rounded-full` on containers (only on avatars/badges)
- Use border-radius > 16px on any element
- Stack sections without adequate spacing (min `py-16`)

